6, in the village of Tarabin in the South, after being shot by police officers during an operation to arrest suspects. Police stated he was suspected of prior acts of vandalism and endangered forces, while his family denied these claims and described the incident as \"cold-blooded murder.\" The officer who fired the shot has been arrested and is under investigation.","review_status":"flagged_for_review","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2026-01-01_2026-05-13","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2026-01-01_2026-05-13","run_id":"canonical","case_index":101}